00:16:04.630 --> 00:16:13.919
Do you reject it? I said you harness it. You don't embrace it like a friend; you harness it like a tool.

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:20.847
Does that make sense? You don't embrace it; you harness it. And you wield it.

00:16:20.848 --> 00:16:27.599
You're like you're cutting with the saw or whatever. There'll be things in it that'll be a blessing to you in the days ahead.

00:16:27.600 --> 00:16:37.910
