00:16:37.911 --> 00:16:57.387
And know that you don't let it all in your house and let it start teaching your kids spiritual things or whatever, or asking it counsel or advice about whatever, but you just know it's a surface thing. You touch it like it's hot, and that's hot.

00:16:57.388 --> 00:17:09.149
Well, I gotta, you know, I don't know how else to describe it to y'all because there's so many people that will have the cure for something that you're overcoming and you'll die, and the Lord's trying to help you.

00:17:09.150 --> 00:17:16.078
Well, God is always going to use something else. I don't know, God's sovereign. He'll use whatever He wants to use.

00:17:16.079 --> 00:17:26.249
But I'm not going to put Him in a box and say, "God, you have to do exactly what I want you to do because this is what makes me feel comfortable."I'm with Him.

00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:32.483
If it comes out the cure for autism, you can know that Brandon Biggs is going to be standing, the first one in line, to help my little girl.

00:17:32.484 --> 00:17:40.994
If there's no strings attached and they're not telling me to do something weird, and it's just like, "You take this and this, and it'll help your little girl,"you know good and well I'll be there.

00:17:40.995 --> 00:17:45.937
You know what I'm saying? Especially if you've been overcoming something for so long.

00:17:45.938 --> 00:17:51.678
I'm standing by faith. So if God wants to use it through medical science, then whatever it takes.

00:17:51.679 --> 00:17:54.910
I don't limit God, and I don't put Him in a box when it comes to things.

00:17:54.911 --> 00:17:59.549
Ladies and gentlemen, I know that He is... Whatever is good comes from God.

00:17:59.550 --> 00:18:06.558
And if it's a cure for something, it's coming from... You didn't get that knowledge on your own.

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:09.678
Even if it's a computer giving it to you, you didn't get it on your own.

00:18:09.679 --> 00:18:15.735
Everything good comes from God, remember that. And everything bad comes from the devil.

00:18:15.736 --> 00:18:21.528
There's no good in the devil. There's no good in him at all. There's no bad in God.

00:18:21.529 --> 00:18:26.532
There's no bad in Him at all. He is a good God, and the devil is a bad devil.

00:18:26.533 --> 00:18:31.677
So if there's something good that comes out of something, you know it's a good God that gives it.

00:18:31.678 --> 00:18:42.698
But there's never a bad thing that comes out of a good God. He's always good, and the devil's always bad. The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:18:42.699 --> 00:18:51.356
And the Bible says that God comes that you may have life and life more abundantly, to the extreme, until it overflows.

00:18:51.357 --> 00:19:01.038
So, anything that comes from anything, I'm always going to give God praise and glory for it, even if it's coming from AI.

00:19:01.039 --> 00:19:12.016
Thank you, Lord, that you can use what the devil means for bad to turn it for good in my favor in finances, in health, and wisdom, whatever it may be.

00:19:12.017 --> 00:19:16.195
Goodness comes from my God. Does that make sense, what I'm telling y'all?

00:19:16.196 --> 00:19:20.237
Because I think people are going to get real flaky about all this.

00:19:20.238 --> 00:19:27.975
But am I going to let a machine be a surrogate for my baby? Heavens, no! I'm not going to let a machine...

00:19:27.976 --> 00:19:40.719
"Well, I couldn't have a baby, so I'm going to put my egg and my sperm in there, and we're going to grow this baby, and we're going to put it in this lab thing."No, that's not the way I'm going to... Heavens, no! I do not believe that's God.

00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:53.788
AI-created things, splice and genetics, make what I saw—making one stronger or making it skinnier or making better genes in the future and making blue eyes—I'm not going to manipulate nature.

00:19:53.789 --> 00:19:58.098
That's weird. That's demonic. You know, that's not God at all.

00:19:58.099 --> 00:20:05.111
I don't believe that's God at all. You're trying to play God, and that's a dangerous thing to do.

00:20:05.112 --> 00:20:13.159
So, I saw that, and I saw the baseball stadiums that will be called, instead of sporting events, they'll be glory events.

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:19.460
And I'm excited about that part, and having this opportunity to bring in the lost for Jesus.

00:20:19.461 --> 00:20:31.013
He's given us one last window—this last call, this last window—to bring in the lost, all for Jesus. Folks, it's all hands on deck right now.

00:20:31.014 --> 00:20:41.086
As we see the earthquakes, as we see these things, as the days are going to get darker and darker, it's going to get so dark that it'll be gross darkness covering the earth.

00:20:41.087 --> 00:20:55.698
But the rest of the scripture says, "Arise and shine, for your light has come, and the glory of the Lord is risen on us."Because when it gets darker over there, it's going to get lighter on us, and Jesus is going to shine the brightest.

00:20:55.699 --> 00:21:05.194
And who's going to be the ones? Just like I told you at the beginning, the people who don't deserve it—it's all about grace.

00:21:05.195 --> 00:21:11.813
And watch what He does with the healings and the demonstrations and saying, "Listen, I'm giving you enough money.

00:21:11.814 --> 00:21:17.475
Now go pay that lady's mortgage off. You want me to pay her house off?

00:21:17.476 --> 00:21:21.859
Yeah, I want you to go show her my love and tell her Jesus loves her.

00:21:21.860 --> 00:21:30.079
Go pay the house off, or go pay her car off, or go and buy her a month's worth of groceries."But you can't do it when you're broke.

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:33.686
Just like when He came to me and He told me about the church thing, and I told y'all about that.

00:21:33.687 --> 00:21:37.581
He said, "Brandon, I don't have anybody else to ask."Isn't that sad?

